These are the sources of the SMT solver Boolector. To compile issue
'./configure && make'. This will build the library 'libboolector.a' and the
solver 'boolector'. The python API can be compiled by issuing
'./configure -python && make', for further details please refer to
'api/python/README'.

For a documentation of Boolector and its public APIs see 'doc/index.html'.

The file VERSION contains the current version number.

The file NEWS lists history and latest changes.

THESE SOURCES ARE FOR ACADEMIC USE ONLY.
USE IN COMPETITIONS IS RESTRICTED TOO.
SEE 'COPYING' FOR MORE DETAILS.

a more recent version of Boolector might be found at

  http://fmv.jku.at/boolector

This site may also contain more documentation.
